        {"🧢 Cross Cap Manifold", "local u = (i / n) * pi\nlocal v = (i % 14) / 14 * pi\nx = 14 * sin(u) * sin(2 * v)\nz = 14 * sin(2 * u) * cos(v) * cos(v)\ny = 14 * sin(u) * sin(u) * cos(2 * v)"},
